data.title: Contact Me Today for a Free Quote
data.meta_description: Contact Blake Austin for your insurance needs in Lexington. He can help you with auto, home, life, and farm insurance products and services.
data.text: After graduating from the University of South Carolina Aiken, I was an assistant golf pro at Woodside Plantation for three years before moving back to Barnwell to work for Farm Bureau Insurance. I started my career as an agent with Farm Bureau Insurance on June 1, 2003. I reside in Barnwell with my wife Lindsay, and our sons, Cameron and Cayson. When I am not working, I enjoy playing golf and watching my sons participate in all of their activities.
